<h1>A matching ride offer was posted</h1>

<p>Hi,</p>

<p>Good news! A new ride offer was posted that matches your request for the event "<strong><%= @ride_request.event.name %></strong>".</p>

<p><a href="<%= event_offer_url(@offer.event, @offer, locale: I18n.locale) %>" class="button">View the offer</a></p>

<p>If the button doesn't work, copy this link into your browser:</p>
<div class="secret-link"><a href="<%= event_offer_url(@offer.event, @offer, locale: I18n.locale) %>"><%= event_offer_url(@offer.event, @offer, locale: I18n.locale) %></a></div>

<p>There may be more offers as well — see all offers for this event here:</p>

<p><a href="<%= event_url(@ride_request.event, locale: I18n.locale) %>"><%= event_url(@ride_request.event, locale: I18n.locale) %></a></p>

<p>If you no longer want to receive notifications for this request, you can delete it with this secret link:</p>

<% destroy_url = event_ride_request_destroy_url(@ride_request.event, @ride_request, token: @ride_request.token, locale: I18n.locale) %>
<p><a href="<%= destroy_url %>" class="button">Delete ride request</a></p>

<p>If the button doesn't work, copy this link into your browser:</p>
<div class="secret-link"><a href="<%= destroy_url %>"><%= destroy_url %></a></div>

<p class="signoff">Kind regards from the HopHub platform.</p>
